name: Barong Bangkung Samurai Boy
description:
Barong bangkung, which is usually black, is a replica of a wild hog’s that usually performed during Ngelawang, a street performance show performed by children and teenagers. Ngelawang is considered an important ritual to drive away demons and bad spirits in Balinese houses.
Now my Boy here is a fusion of Balinese and Japanese's Samurai Culture. Please welcome Barong Bangkung Samurai Boy
